product_name: NYX Professional MakeupFat Oil Lip Drip Vegan Lip Oil
summary: SummaryHighlightsCruelty FreeGive BackServe high-shine looks sans stickiness with Fat Oil Lip Drip from NYX Professional Makeup - the vegan lip oil that delivers up to 12 hours of hydration
details: DetailsBenefitsThe fan favorite Lip Oil just got elevated with 6 NEW creamy shades!Serve high-shine looks sans stickiness with Fat Oil Lip Drip‚ÄîAmerica's #1 Lip Oil!Wear your tinted lip gloss solo for a soft hint of color, or pair it with your favorite NYX Professional Makeup lip color for added intensity.Available in 8 universally flattering shades, and 6 creamy shades this lip oil features an extra large applicator for easy, smooth application, leaving you with a glossy, high shine finishVegan. Cruelty freeItem 2626457How To UseApply lip oil gloss to bare lips for a hint of color and long-lasting hydration. Wear it alone or layer it over lip liner for added color and shine.IngredientsPolyisobutene, Hydrogenated Polyisobutene, Pentaerythrityl Tetraisostearate, Paraffinum Liquidum / Mineral Oil / Huile Minerale, Diisostearyl Malate, Polyglyceryl-3 Diisostearate, Rosa Canina Fruit Oil, Rubus Chamaemorus Seed Oil, Rubus Idaeus Seed Oil / Raspberry Seed Oil, Squalane, Aroma / Flavor, Aluminum Hydroxide, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Dibutyl Ethylhexanoyl Glutamide, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tocopherol, Tocopheryl Acetate, Diethylhexyl Syringylidenemalonate, Sorbic Acid, Phenoxyethanol, CI 15850 / Red 7 Lake, CI 77491 / Iron Oxides, CI 77492 / Iron Oxides, CI 77499 / Iron Oxides, CI 77891 / Titanium Dioxide, CI 19140 / Yellow 5 Lake, Benzyl Alcohol (F.I.L. N70042120/1).
how_to_use: Apply lip oil gloss to bare lips for a hint of color and long-lasting hydration. Wear it alone or layer it over lip liner for added color and shine.

faceoff_positive.comments: I love it, but i think the one i had was expired, had one specific part that was clumped together, mightve been a mixing issue? but overall i love the lip drip oil, i have two toned lips, one a nice pink and another a pinkish brownish color, and the shade follow back compliments them perfectly. but its a little sticky and it seperates kind of. i have chapped lips because i have a habit of licking them, and this feels hydrating but i dont really get that hydration End result is its a great product and i am going to repurchase it, in the shade Follow Back AND Missed Call üíó
faceoff_positive.headline: Very good!

faceoff_negative.comments: Overall, I love the pigmentation, the way it feels on the lips. I'm literally OBSESSED with this product. BUT I have been needing to purchase new ones, due to the applicator not being long enough to grab the product at the bottom. Plenty of product left over at the top as well, at first I thought it was user error but it happens to every single one I have, and my sisters also have the same issues. Besides that the product is amazing.
faceoff_negative.headline: Great but the applicator sucks
